---
// Technology.astro — DS-09 (Option A)
---

<section id="technology" class="relative bg-section">
  <div class="rule-cyan"></div>

  <div class="max-w-content mx-auto px-6 md:px-12 py-20 md:py-[120px]">

    <!-- Header -->
    <div class="reveal mb-16">
      <p class="font-mono font-semibold text-[18px] text-cyan uppercase tracking-[0.2em] mb-4">TECHNOLOGY & INFRASTRUCTURE</p>
      <h2 class="font-grotesk font-bold text-off-white mb-5" style="font-size: clamp(32px, 4.5vw, 48px); letter-spacing: -0.02em; max-width: 640px;">
        Built on technology that already works at scale.
      </h2>
      <p class="font-grotesk text-mid-grey text-lg" style="max-width: 600px; line-height: 1.65;">
        DigiSite doesn't build screens, content platforms, or programmatic marketplaces &mdash; that technology already exists. We deploy it in a location category it has never reached before.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Section image -->
    <div class="reveal mb-[72px] overflow-hidden rounded-md">
      <img
        src="/technology-install.jpeg"
        alt="DigiSite screen cleanly installed on scaffolding in a UK city centre during daytime"
        width="1536"
        height="1024"
        loading="lazy"
        class="w-full h-[480px] md:h-[680px] object-cover"
      />
    </div>

    <!-- Three-column grid -->
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6 reveal-stagger">

      <!-- Display Hardware -->
      <div class="reveal p-8 md:p-10 border border-cyan/[0.12] rounded bg-cyan/[0.02]">
        <p class="font-mono font-semibold text-[13px] uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-cyan mb-4">DISPLAY HARDWARE</p>
        <h3 class="font-grotesk font-bold text-[22px] text-off-white mb-4">High-brightness outdoor LED</h3>
        <p class="font-grotesk text-[15px] text-mid-grey mb-6" style="line-height: 1.65;">
          DigiScaff uses Hikvision DS-D4257GO-2AAA panels &mdash; 9,000 nit brightness, IP66 weatherproofed, 100,000-hour LED lifespan. DigiPerim uses Dynamo DVO Series panels, purpose-built for perimeter fence applications with full front-access maintenance. Both run on 960&times;960mm modular cabinets, fully replaceable in the field.
        </p>
        <p class="font-mono text-[11px] text-cyan/70" style="line-height: 1.6;">
          9,000 nits &middot; IP66 &middot; 100,000hr lifespan<br>
          P5.7 (DigiScaff) &middot; P8 (DigiPerim)
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Content & Data -->
      <div class="reveal p-8 md:p-10 border border-cyan/[0.12] rounded bg-cyan/[0.02]">
        <p class="font-mono font-semibold text-[13px] uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-cyan mb-4">CONTENT & AUDIENCE DATA</p>
        <h3 class="font-grotesk font-bold text-[22px] text-off-white mb-4">Remote control. Verified audiences.</h3>
        <p class="font-grotesk text-[15px] text-mid-grey mb-6" style="line-height: 1.65;">
          Every screen is managed remotely via Navori QL &mdash; a commercial DOOH CMS running on BrightSign XT244 media players. Multi-advertiser campaign scheduling, content rotation, proof-of-play reporting, and live health monitoring from a single cloud dashboard. At scale, DigiSite migrates to Broadsign Control with its built-in Reach SSP. Audience measurement is powered by Route, the UK's Joint Industry Currency for OOH.
        </p>
        <p class="font-mono text-[11px] text-cyan/70" style="line-height: 1.6;">
          Route data &middot; 400,000+ sites measured<br>
          Navori QL &middot; BrightSign XT244 &middot; proof-of-play verified
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Marketplace -->
      <div class="reveal p-8 md:p-10 border border-cyan/[0.12] rounded bg-cyan/[0.02]">
        <p class="font-mono font-semibold text-[13px] uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-cyan mb-4">ADVERTISING MARKETPLACE</p>
        <h3 class="font-grotesk font-bold text-[22px] text-off-white mb-4">Connected to every major media buyer.</h3>
        <p class="font-grotesk text-[15px] text-mid-grey mb-6" style="line-height: 1.65;">
          DigiSite inventory is accessible through the programmatic DOOH marketplace via Vistar Media and Hivestack SSPs &mdash; connecting DigiSite screens to demand-side platforms used by every major media agency and brand buying team. At scale, Broadsign's built-in Reach SSP replaces standalone SSP relationships. Unsold inventory fills automatically. Direct campaigns book at full rate.
        </p>
        <p class="font-mono text-[11px] text-cyan/70" style="line-height: 1.6;">
          Vistar Media &middot; Hivestack<br>
          Open Exchange &middot; PMP &middot; Programmatic Guaranteed
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Bottom statement -->
    <div class="reveal text-center mt-[72px]">
      <p class="font-grotesk font-bold text-[24px] text-off-white" style="letter-spacing: -0.01em;">
        The infrastructure exists. The inventory category doesn't &mdash; yet.
      </p>
    </div>

  </div>
</section>
